        <p>We believe in the importance and the key role of music in the Church. Worship in a modern style and focused
            on Jesus is an essential part of our celebrations.</p>

        <p>We want to allow each one to meet God through worship and allow Him to manifest Himself as we give Him space
            to move. We desire to see an open heaven, lives transformed and sickness healed in the tangible presence of
            God. The values we focus on in our worship teams are excellence, dedication to God, listening to the Holy
            Spirit and service. Our vision is also to train musicians, singers and technicians in worship ministry, and
            share with them what God has given us for years as well as equip them for service.</p>

        <p>Our different groups are invited on a regular basis to lead worship in various events in Switzerland and in
            Europe. Many musicians serving in the Gospel Center Lausanne also play in other groups outside of church.
            The Gospel Center Lausanne encourages musicians in their gifts wherever they go. We want to create a
            platform where they feel good and can develop themselves in their full potential.</p>

        <p>Leading music in the church is our greatest privileged; we believe great things are ahead of us ! The best is
            yet to come !</p>

